overview.en: SporeOcean is the next-generation decentralized financial network developed on the basis of Substrate. SporeOcean attempts to adopt the distinctions of DeFi and NFT to chain and scale the real-world asset, empower a series of innovative encrypted financial products so as to open the gate for traditional finance, thus allow new capital to flow into the WEB 3.0 crypto ecosystem.
overview.zh: SporeOcean是基于Substrate开发的下一代去中化金融网络。 SporeOcean希望利用DeFi、NFT的特点，将真实世界资产上链规模化，赋能一系列创新加密金融产品为传统金融打开闸门，让新的资本涌入WEB 3.0加密生态系统。
